325
00:27:32,040 --> 00:27:34,040
What? Okay, fine.

326
00:27:34,040 --> 00:27:37,540
Hello, えー、みなさん。Old senpai, Mori Calliope desu. Yay!
Hello, um, everyone. I'm the old senpai, Mori Calliope. Yay!

