00:27:49,540 --> 00:27:52,540
Pink, kind of! Of course, different shades of pink, right?

333
00:27:52,540 --> 00:27:59,040
Yeah, the colors are so important in this life, so we must say that this is the pink team, right?

334
00:27:59,040 --> 00:28:00,540
Pink team!

335
00:28:00,540 --> 00:28:02,540
Pink-purple team!

336
00:28:02,540 --> 00:28:05,540
Pink-purple team! よろしくお願いいたします。
