Nice, wonderful! But you know, the lighting actually when we were singing the song that we just sang a moment ago was blue.

339
00:28:12,540 --> 00:28:16,040
Yeah, was blue. So pretty, right? Look at that.

340
00:28:16,040 --> 00:28:19,540
What kind of emotion do you think the blue represents?

