00:28:27,040 --> 00:28:32,540
ちょっとそういう悲しいみたいなイメージはあるけど、でも、綺麗なイメージもあるよ。
...or having a sad image, but it also has a beautiful image too.

345
00:28:32,540 --> 00:28:35,040
Yeah, also beautiful. Sad, lonely, also beautiful.

346
00:28:35,040 --> 00:28:41,040
For Calliope, I think sometimes maybe there's some fear, right? 怖さ。A little scary, right?
For Calliope, I think sometimes maybe there's some fear, right? Fear. A little scary, right?

347
00:28:41,040 --> 00:28:46,040
But, you know, emotions are beautiful, right? 感情がめっちゃ美しいと思う。Right?
But, you know, emotions are beautiful, right? I think emotions are really beautiful. Right?

348
00:28:46,040 --> 00:28:51,040
So positive, negative, either way, I think colors are really beautiful.

349
00:28:51,040 --> 00:28:56,040
I agree with you! And you know, even if sometimes we have fear and we're scared of doing something, maybe...

350
00:28:56,040 --> 00:29:00,040
maybe we should overcome, we should do our best to, you know...

351
00:29:00,040 --> 00:29:03,040
怖くても、we have to do our best, right? 頑張らないといけないね。
Even if we're scared, we have to do our best, right? We have to keep trying.

352
00:29:03,040 --> 00:29:04,040
Yes!

353
