368
00:30:02,548 --> 00:30:03,548
Yeah!

369
00:30:03,548 --> 00:30:05,848
かっこいいね！ おおー！
That's so cool! Oh wow!

370
00:30:05,848 --> 00:30:09,548
ラオラ意味深い。Deep meaning! That's cool!
Raora, that was so deep! Deep meaning! That's cool!

371
00:30:09,548 --> 00:30:10,548
かっこいい
Cool.

372
00:30:10,548 --> 00:30:13,848
かっこいいね！ Cute and cool, Raora.
So cool! Cute and cool, Raora.

373
00:30:13,848 --> 00:30:15,048
No, no, no!

374
00:30:15,048 --> 00:30:17,048
You are cool!

375
00:30:17,048 --> 00:30:19,548
Everyone here is cool! みんなクール！
Everyone here is cool! Everyone's cool!

376
00:30:19,548 --> 00:30:24,048
Team Pink is very cool. Pink is a cool color, okay?

377
00:30:24,048 --> 00:30:26,548
Well, happy birthday to you.

378
00:30:26,548 --> 00:30:28,048
Thank you so much, Mori-sama.

379
00:30:28,048 --> 00:30:30,548
お誕生日おめでとう！ Happy birthday!
Happy birthday! Happy birthday!

380
00:30:30,548 --> 00:30:33,548
