381
00:30:33,548 --> 00:30:41,548
It's a very meaningful song and I really appreciate to have my dai-senpais with me. Thank you so much!
It's a very meaningful song and I really appreciate to have my great senpais with me. Thank you so much!

382
00:30:41,548 --> 00:30:45,548
Yeah, of course, old senpais. Old senpais here with you.

383
00:30:45,548 --> 00:30:50,048
Well, myself and Towa gotta get out of here, but Raora, you keep on keeping on, okay?

384
00:30:50,048 --> 00:30:52,048
Okay, I'll do my best!

385
00:30:52,048 --> 00:30:53,848
Yeah, and we'll see you guys later, okay?

386
00:30:53,848 --> 00:30:55,248
See you guys later!

387
00:30:55,248 --> 00:30:59,048
Bye everybody! See ya! Bye-bye!

388
00:31:27,048 --> 00:31:31,548
白い世界の中では
In this white world,

389
00:31:31,548 --> 00:31:38,248
時間が止まってゆくような気がした
it felt like time was stopping.

390
00:31:38,248 --> 00:31:44,248
いつも見せないような表情が
That expression you never seemed to show me...

391
00:31:44,248 --> 00:31:51,248
その距離が 少しだけ愛しかった
I loved that distance, just a little.

392
00:31:51,248 --> 00:31:55,048
巻き戻せないと
"It can't be rewound,"

393
00:31:55,048 --> 00:31:57,248
はしゃいでいるその横顔
you said, looking so cheerful.

394
00:31:57,248 --> 00:32:00,048
抱えていた悩みも ちっぽけだ
Even the troubles I carried felt so small.

395
00:32:00,048 --> 00:32:03,248
君に染まる視界が
This view painted in your colors,

396
00:32:03,248 --> 00:32:08,048
かじかんでく両手が
these hands frozen with cold...

397
00:32:08,048 --> 00:32:16,248
心から願うよ 終わらせたくなどはないんだと
I wish from the bottom of my heart that this will never end.

398
00:32:16,248 --> 00:32:22,548
思い出の中にはいつも君の姿
